data.description: Motivated Seller! Beautiful Home in MAJESTIC OAKS that upon entering the lovely Doors, one not only feels the warmth but, notes that the foyer opens up to the great room with the formal dining area to the right.   Home features a spacious 2,182 sqft split floor plan, three bedrooms, 2.5 bath and a spacious eat-in kitchen and a newer upgraded water softner.   The enclosed Florida room is perfect for family room, game room as the potential is your vision.   All of the bedrooms offer oversized walk-in closets and bring a lot of natural light.  Home also features a newer air conditioning unit which was installed in 2021, and a new stove in 2022.  In April of 2023 a new Hot Water Heater was installed and in May of 2023, had roof replacement.   With the privacy fence and beautiful shade trees, the relaxing aura is noted.   Home also features an attached storage room (back of house), for storage during the colder months.
